650
00:21:54,564 --> 00:21:56,274
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm sorry to drop
by unannounced,</i></b></font>

651
00:21:56,358 --> 00:21:57,734
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I need to
talk to you.</i></b></font>

652
00:21:57,859 --> 00:22:00,529
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, no. I'm sorry that I had
to leave a little bit early.</i></b></font>

653
00:22:00,612 --> 00:22:02,990
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just wanted to get the
place ready for when
Mike gets home.</i></b></font>

654
00:22:03,073 --> 00:22:04,783
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then I won't take up
much of your time.</i></b></font>

655
00:22:06,076 --> 00:22:07,744
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They offered Leonard
Bailey a deal.</i></b></font>

656
00:22:08,370 --> 00:22:09,705
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How long?
Seven years.</i></b></font>

657
00:22:09,788 --> 00:22:11,498
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I can probably get
them down to five.</i></b></font>

658
00:22:11,957 --> 00:22:13,750
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Five more years for
a crime he didn't commit</i></b></font>

659
00:22:13,834 --> 00:22:14,876
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>doesn't seem
really fair.</i></b></font>

660
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:16,169
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And losing a retrial</i></b></font>

661
00:22:16,253 --> 00:22:18,296
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and dying in prison
doesn't seem fair either.</i></b></font>

662
00:22:18,422 --> 00:22:20,507
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But we're not
going to lose.
That's not true.</i></b></font>

663
00:22:20,590 --> 00:22:22,676
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>There's a good
chance we will.</i></b></font>

664
00:22:22,759 --> 00:22:24,302
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Jessica.
Rachel.</i></b></font>

665
00:22:24,386 --> 00:22:25,679
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Juries are
unpredictable.</i></b></font>

666
00:22:26,263 --> 00:22:28,181
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Even if they've been told
to disregard something,</i></b></font>

667
00:22:28,265 --> 00:22:30,392
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>they know he was
convicted before.</i></b></font>

668
00:22:31,018 --> 00:22:33,186
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>This is a chance at
getting his life back.</i></b></font>

669
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:35,355
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What kind of life are
we talking about?</i></b></font>

670
00:22:35,439 --> 00:22:37,524
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He's still going to be
seen as a murderer,</i></b></font>

671
00:22:37,607 --> 00:22:39,901
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>even by the closest thing
he has to a mother.</i></b></font>

672
00:22:39,985 --> 00:22:42,195
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not going to let him die
for a crime he didn't commit.</i></b></font>

673
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:43,530
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't want to let
him die, either.</i></b></font>

674
00:22:43,613 --> 00:22:45,407
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want to fight
to get him out.</i></b></font>

675
00:22:45,490 --> 00:22:47,159
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I don't think you've
been practicing law</i></b></font>

676
00:22:47,242 --> 00:22:49,202
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>long enough to
make that call.</i></b></font>

677
00:22:49,786 --> 00:22:51,913
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Rachel, this is
a win for him.</i></b></font>

678
00:22:52,039 --> 00:22:53,165
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, get your
mind right</i></b></font>

679
00:22:53,248 --> 00:22:55,876
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>so that we can walk into
that prison on the same page.</i></b></font>

680
00:23:02,966 --> 00:23:04,176
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey.</i></b></font>

681
00:23:04,801 --> 00:23:06,219
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Unless you're
here to tell me</i></b></font>

682
00:23:06,303 --> 00:23:08,221
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you've come to your
senses about this animal,</i></b></font>

683
00:23:08,305 --> 00:23:10,015
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>this is going to be
a short conversation.</i></b></font>

684
00:23:10,098 --> 00:23:11,475
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I came here to
show you this.</i></b></font>

685
00:23:12,267 --> 00:23:13,977
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What is this?
It's a three-year</i></b></font>

686
00:23:14,061 --> 00:23:15,729
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>surveillance agreement
with the best</i></b></font>

687
00:23:15,812 --> 00:23:17,689
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>detective agency
in the state.</i></b></font>

688
00:23:19,274 --> 00:23:21,401
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And what makes you think just
because you follow him,</i></b></font>

689
00:23:21,485 --> 00:23:23,612
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>it's going stop him from
committing crimes?</i></b></font>

690
00:23:23,695 --> 00:23:25,864
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Cameron, I can't have
him in there with Mike.</i></b></font>

691
00:23:25,947 --> 00:23:27,324
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, from what I heard,
Mike's getting out.</i></b></font>

692
00:23:27,407 --> 00:23:28,700
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's not that simple.</i></b></font>

693
00:23:28,784 --> 00:23:30,285
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you mean
it's not that simple?</i></b></font>

694
00:23:30,452 --> 00:23:31,661
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>(SIGHS)</i></b></font>

695
00:23:32,412 --> 00:23:35,499
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The SEC pulled
some shady shit
with Mike's cellmate.</i></b></font>

696
00:23:35,582 --> 00:23:38,543
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>The same guy that
helped get Mike out
in the first place.</i></b></font>

697
00:23:38,627 --> 00:23:42,089
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now, Mike's been
playing chicken with them
and if he doesn't drop it,</i></b></font>

698
00:23:42,172 --> 00:23:43,548
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>they're not going
to let him out.</i></b></font>

699
00:23:43,757 --> 00:23:45,175
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Let me get
this straight.</i></b></font>

700
00:23:45,342 --> 00:23:47,135
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You want me
to perjure myself</i></b></font>

701
00:23:47,219 --> 00:23:49,471
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>so you can put this
monster on the street</i></b></font>

702
00:23:49,554 --> 00:23:52,724
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because your sidekick
wants to fight the man?</i></b></font>

703
00:23:52,808 --> 00:23:54,184
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Don't play that
shit with me.</i></b></font>

704
00:23:54,267 --> 00:23:56,103
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You've been
crossing lines for years</i></b></font>

705
00:23:56,186 --> 00:23:57,687
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and you didn't lose
a minute's sleep over it.</i></b></font>

706
00:23:57,771 --> 00:23:59,481
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're damn right I didn't,
because I was doing it</i></b></font>

707
00:23:59,564 --> 00:24:01,691
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to put guys like
Gallo away.</i></b></font>

708
00:24:01,775 --> 00:24:04,444
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Not let them wander around
at night hoping some fat guy</i></b></font>

709
00:24:04,528 --> 00:24:06,947
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>with a Polaroid is
going to keep them from
murdering somebody else.</i></b></font>

710
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:08,240
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And what if that person</i></b></font>

711
00:24:08,323 --> 00:24:10,200
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he was going to be
murdering was me?</i></b></font>

712
00:24:10,283 --> 00:24:13,870
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because Mike is to me
what I used to be to you.</i></b></font>

713
00:24:15,038 --> 00:24:17,290
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then convince him to
do the right thing</i></b></font>

714
00:24:17,374 --> 00:24:19,126
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>like you tried to do
once with me.</i></b></font>

715
00:24:19,209 --> 00:24:20,585
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because, Harvey,</i></b></font>

716
00:24:20,669 --> 00:24:23,213
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you know what you're doing
with Gallo is wrong.</i></b></font>

717
00:24:35,517 --> 00:24:36,560
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey.</i></b></font>

718
00:24:36,643 --> 00:24:37,644
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're not going
to believe this,</i></b></font>

719
00:24:37,727 --> 00:24:39,146
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I got Rachel on
the phone for you.</i></b></font>

720
00:24:39,229 --> 00:24:40,605
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What?
Yeah.</i></b></font>

721
00:24:40,689 --> 00:24:41,690
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She had my number from
the other night</i></b></font>

722
00:24:41,773 --> 00:24:42,816
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and she wants
to talk to you.</i></b></font>

723
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:44,985
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks.</i></b></font>

724
00:24:45,068 --> 00:24:46,236
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And, Mike,</i></b></font>

725
00:24:46,319 --> 00:24:47,821
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>if you're staying
in here for me,</i></b></font>

726
00:24:47,904 --> 00:24:49,156
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>don't do it.</i></b></font>

727
00:24:55,495 --> 00:24:56,538
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey.</i></b></font>

728
00:24:56,621 --> 00:24:58,039
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>God, I can't
wait to see you.</i></b></font>

729
00:24:58,248 --> 00:24:59,791
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't wait
to see you either.</i></b></font>

730
00:25:00,584 --> 00:25:01,793
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Are you okay?</i></b></font>

731
00:25:02,377 --> 00:25:04,337
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah. I, um...</i></b></font>

732
00:25:04,921 --> 00:25:06,965
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just wanted to talk to you
about my death row client.</i></b></font>

733
00:25:08,049 --> 00:25:09,301
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How can I help?</i></b></font>

734
00:25:09,384 --> 00:25:10,677
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They offered us a deal</i></b></font>

735
00:25:10,760 --> 00:25:12,304
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>for him to get out
in five years</i></b></font>

736
00:25:12,387 --> 00:25:13,722
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and Jessica wants to take it.</i></b></font>

737
00:25:14,556 --> 00:25:16,683
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I want to
fight for him.</i></b></font>

738
00:25:17,017 --> 00:25:19,436
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Let me guess, she wants
to present a united front.</i></b></font>

739
00:25:19,811 --> 00:25:21,104
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>She does.</i></b></font>

740
00:25:22,105 --> 00:25:23,690
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, I'm not sure
how I can help you</i></b></font>

741
00:25:23,773 --> 00:25:25,734
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>other than to tell you
to follow your gut.</i></b></font>

742
00:25:26,401 --> 00:25:27,444
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You can</i></b></font>

743
00:25:27,527 --> 00:25:29,863
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>help me understand what
it's like to be in prison.</i></b></font>

744
00:25:36,703 --> 00:25:38,038
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You better be
convincing up there.</i></b></font>

745
00:25:38,121 --> 00:25:40,540
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Gallo, I'm about
to sell my soul
to make us even.</i></b></font>

746
00:25:40,624 --> 00:25:42,292
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, sit down,
shut up,</i></b></font>

747
00:25:42,375 --> 00:25:43,585
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and make sure that,
after today,</i></b></font>

748
00:25:43,668 --> 00:25:45,086
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I never see
your face again.</i></b></font>

749
00:25:45,420 --> 00:25:46,630
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mr. Specter,</i></b></font>

750
00:25:46,713 --> 00:25:47,964
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>are you ready
to be sworn in?</i></b></font>

751
00:25:49,174 --> 00:25:50,717
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Ladies and gentlemen
of the Board,</i></b></font>

752
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:52,969
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>before Mr. Specter
testifies,</i></b></font>

753
00:25:53,053 --> 00:25:54,721
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'd like to present
Michael Ross</i></b></font>

754
00:25:54,804 --> 00:25:56,681
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>as a witness on
behalf of the State.</i></b></font>

755
00:25:56,765 --> 00:25:59,100
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mr. Chairman, this hearing
was called so that
I could prove...</i></b></font>

756
00:25:59,184 --> 00:26:00,560
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You'll get your chance,
Mr. Specter.</i></b></font>

757
00:26:00,644 --> 00:26:02,437
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'd like to hear what
the young man has to say.</i></b></font>

758
00:26:04,731 --> 00:26:06,066
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>CAMERON: Could I
have him sworn in?</i></b></font>

759
00:26:06,149 --> 00:26:07,484
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>PAROLE BOARD CHAIR:
That won't be necessary.</i></b></font>

760
00:26:08,568 --> 00:26:10,278
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mr. Ross, you
are an inmate</i></b></font>

761
00:26:10,403 --> 00:26:12,155
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>here at Danbury,
is that correct?
Yes.</i></b></font>

762
00:26:12,239 --> 00:26:13,907
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm serving
a two-year sentence</i></b></font>

763
00:26:13,990 --> 00:26:15,575
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>for practicing law
without a license.</i></b></font>

764
00:26:15,659 --> 00:26:17,118
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And what firm
did you work at?</i></b></font>

765
00:26:17,827 --> 00:26:19,204
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I worked for
Mr. Specter.</i></b></font>

766
00:26:19,579 --> 00:26:21,289
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Are you aware
that Mr. Specter</i></b></font>

767
00:26:21,373 --> 00:26:23,667
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>originally prosecuted
Frank Gallo?</i></b></font>

768
00:26:23,833 --> 00:26:24,918
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes, I am.</i></b></font>

769
00:26:25,001 --> 00:26:26,336
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And who made you
aware of that?</i></b></font>

770
00:26:27,170 --> 00:26:28,505
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Frank Gallo did.</i></b></font>

771
00:26:29,005 --> 00:26:31,049
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He just mentioned
something in passing?</i></b></font>

772
00:26:31,341 --> 00:26:32,467
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No.</i></b></font>

773
00:26:33,176 --> 00:26:35,178
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, on my first night here,
Mr. Gallo bribed a guard</i></b></font>

774
00:26:35,262 --> 00:26:36,554
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>so that he could
get into my cell</i></b></font>

775
00:26:36,638 --> 00:26:38,348
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and then he pretended
to be my roommate.</i></b></font>

776
00:26:38,431 --> 00:26:40,433
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And after getting
me to trust him,</i></b></font>

777
00:26:40,517 --> 00:26:42,435
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he told me that he had been
trying to get revenge</i></b></font>

778
00:26:42,519 --> 00:26:44,646
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>on Harvey Specter since the
day he'd been put away.</i></b></font>

779
00:26:44,729 --> 00:26:45,939
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And he told me that now,</i></b></font>

780
00:26:46,022 --> 00:26:48,608
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he was going to get revenge on
Harvey by coming after me.</i></b></font>

781
00:26:48,692 --> 00:26:51,486
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Was it clear to you what he
meant by "coming after you"?</i></b></font>

782
00:26:52,195 --> 00:26:53,530
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He said he
would kill me.</i></b></font>

783
00:26:54,030 --> 00:26:55,448
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>In fact, he tried to shiv me</i></b></font>

784
00:26:55,532 --> 00:26:58,368
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>the second night,
but a guard stopped him.</i></b></font>

785
00:26:58,910 --> 00:27:00,161
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Just one more question.</i></b></font>

786
00:27:00,245 --> 00:27:02,956
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Was Mr. Specter aware
of these threats?</i></b></font>

787
00:27:04,040 --> 00:27:05,333
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Of course he was.</i></b></font>

788
00:27:06,209 --> 00:27:08,545
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why else do you think
he's been trying
to get Gallo parole?</i></b></font>

789
00:27:10,338 --> 00:27:11,715
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thank you, Mr. Ross.</i></b></font>

790
00:27:14,009 --> 00:27:15,302
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mr. Specter,
are you prepared</i></b></font>

791
00:27:15,385 --> 00:27:17,304
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to refute this
testimony under oath?</i></b></font>

792
00:27:18,805 --> 00:27:20,181
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, Your Honor.</i></b></font>

793
00:27:20,265 --> 00:27:21,558
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not.</i></b></font>

794
00:27:22,892 --> 00:27:24,561
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then we'll take a
five-minute recess.</i></b></font>

795
00:27:26,104 --> 00:27:27,397
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You did this.</i></b></font>

796
00:27:27,522 --> 00:27:29,357
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You were in on it with
him the whole time.</i></b></font>

797
00:27:29,441 --> 00:27:31,234
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're right, I did.</i></b></font>

798
00:27:32,402 --> 00:27:34,237
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, you come after me,
not him.</i></b></font>

799
00:27:34,404 --> 00:27:35,572
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm coming after
both of you.</i></b></font>

800
00:27:35,697 --> 00:27:37,032
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But I'm coming after
him sooner.</i></b></font>

801
00:27:37,115 --> 00:27:39,617
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey. You can't
hide from me.</i></b></font>

802
00:27:39,701 --> 00:27:41,411
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, I don't need
to hide from you.</i></b></font>

803
00:27:41,578 --> 00:27:43,330
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>As it turns out
I'm getting out today,</i></b></font>

804
00:27:43,413 --> 00:27:45,081
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and there's nothing
you can do about it.</i></b></font>

805
00:27:52,547 --> 00:27:54,424
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Five years is still
a long time.</i></b></font>

806
00:27:54,758 --> 00:27:56,051
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yes, it is.</i></b></font>

807
00:27:56,551 --> 00:27:57,886
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But then, you walk out
of here a free man.</i></b></font>

808
00:27:57,969 --> 00:27:59,637
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>A free man, but not
an innocent one.</i></b></font>

809
00:27:59,721 --> 00:28:01,264
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're still
innocent, Leonard.</i></b></font>

810
00:28:01,348 --> 00:28:02,974
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Whether the world sees
it that way or not.</i></b></font>

811
00:28:03,058 --> 00:28:05,352
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But if the world thinks
I'm a convicted murderer,</i></b></font>

812
00:28:05,435 --> 00:28:07,395
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>then I might
as well die in here.</i></b></font>

813
00:28:07,771 --> 00:28:08,938
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because there's
not going to be</i></b></font>

814
00:28:09,022 --> 00:28:10,273
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>a life out there
for me, anyway.</i></b></font>

815
00:28:10,648 --> 00:28:12,150
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No one said it was
going to be easy.</i></b></font>

816
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,485
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But there's no point</i></b></font>

817
00:28:13,568 --> 00:28:15,028
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>in dying for a crime
you didn't commit.</i></b></font>

818
00:28:15,111 --> 00:28:16,488
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't think
you understand.</i></b></font>

819
00:28:16,571 --> 00:28:18,698
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not doing this
just to stay alive.</i></b></font>

820
00:28:19,407 --> 00:28:20,700
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm doing this
so one day</i></b></font>

821
00:28:20,784 --> 00:28:22,202
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can knock on my kids' door</i></b></font>

822
00:28:22,285 --> 00:28:23,787
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and they'll know
their father</i></b></font>

823
00:28:23,870 --> 00:28:25,372
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>is an innocent man.</i></b></font>

824
00:28:25,455 --> 00:28:28,375
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If I take this deal, that's
never going to happen.</i></b></font>

825
00:28:28,458 --> 00:28:31,127
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>If you don't take it,
it may never happen either.</i></b></font>

826
00:28:33,880 --> 00:28:35,924
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, you're pretty quiet.
What do you think?</i></b></font>

827
00:28:37,300 --> 00:28:40,387
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I... I think that Jessica
has a lot more experience
than I do.</i></b></font>

828
00:28:40,804 --> 00:28:42,347
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's not what
I asked you.</i></b></font>

829
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:45,892
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I want to know what you
think I should do.</i></b></font>

830
00:28:45,975 --> 00:28:47,769
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Leonard, the odds of
you getting out...</i></b></font>

831
00:28:47,852 --> 00:28:50,605
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I said I want to know
what she thinks.</i></b></font>

832
00:28:57,237 --> 00:28:58,988
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I think you
should fight.</i></b></font>

833
00:29:00,782 --> 00:29:02,450
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Then that's what
I'm going to do.</i></b></font>

834
00:29:06,913 --> 00:29:08,081
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>God damn it.</i></b></font>

835
00:29:08,164 --> 00:29:10,083
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I said we needed to be
on the same page.</i></b></font>

836
00:29:10,166 --> 00:29:12,585
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He asked me what I thought.
I'm not going to lie to him.</i></b></font>

837
00:29:12,669 --> 00:29:15,213
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I never would have
thought Robert Zane's
daughter would be so naive.</i></b></font>

838
00:29:15,296 --> 00:29:16,756
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Naive?</i></b></font>

839
00:29:17,465 --> 00:29:18,758
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was actually starting
to believe that</i></b></font>

840
00:29:18,842 --> 00:29:20,260
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>you cared about this case.</i></b></font>

841
00:29:20,343 --> 00:29:22,178
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But the only thing
that you care about</i></b></font>

842
00:29:22,262 --> 00:29:24,180
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>is putting it to bed as
quickly as possible.</i></b></font>

843
00:29:24,264 --> 00:29:25,723
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>How dare you.</i></b></font>

844
00:29:25,849 --> 00:29:27,559
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Playing the odds isn't
the same as not caring.</i></b></font>

845
00:29:27,642 --> 00:29:28,893
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Maybe not.
But, Jessica,</i></b></font>

846
00:29:28,977 --> 00:29:30,478
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I have watched you
my whole career.</i></b></font>

847
00:29:30,562 --> 00:29:33,148
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And this is the first time
that you've ever backed away
from a fight.</i></b></font>

848
00:29:33,231 --> 00:29:34,607
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's because you've
never seen me fight</i></b></font>

849
00:29:34,691 --> 00:29:36,151
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>when someone's life
is on the line.</i></b></font>

850
00:29:37,110 --> 00:29:38,570
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You...
That's right.</i></b></font>

851
00:29:38,653 --> 00:29:40,947
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I was in a situation like
this once before.</i></b></font>

852
00:29:41,030 --> 00:29:43,116
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I did what you want
me to do now.</i></b></font>

853
00:29:43,283 --> 00:29:44,492
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>We lost.</i></b></font>

854
00:29:44,576 --> 00:29:45,785
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And it ripped me to shreds.</i></b></font>

855
00:29:45,869 --> 00:29:47,287
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, when I tell you</i></b></font>

856
00:29:47,370 --> 00:29:49,664
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I have a lot more
experience than you,</i></b></font>

857
00:29:49,747 --> 00:29:50,832
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>believe it.</i></b></font>

858
00:29:52,459 --> 00:29:54,210
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Jessica, I'm sorry</i></b></font>

859
00:29:55,378 --> 00:29:58,131
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>that you lost a case
like this before.</i></b></font>

860
00:29:59,382 --> 00:30:01,134
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>But the way to help Leonard
is not to convince him</i></b></font>

861
00:30:01,217 --> 00:30:03,052
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to take some deal that
he can't live with.</i></b></font>

862
00:30:03,136 --> 00:30:06,598
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It is to fight to give him
something worth living for.</i></b></font>

863
00:30:18,735 --> 00:30:20,069
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What the hell
did you do?</i></b></font>

864
00:30:20,153 --> 00:30:21,321
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I did what I said I'd do.</i></b></font>

865
00:30:21,404 --> 00:30:22,739
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I kept that
animal behind bars.</i></b></font>

866
00:30:22,822 --> 00:30:24,240
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm talking about Mike.</i></b></font>

867
00:30:24,657 --> 00:30:26,034
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You cut a deal with him,
didn't you?</i></b></font>

868
00:30:26,117 --> 00:30:27,243
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, Harvey.</i></b></font>

869
00:30:27,368 --> 00:30:29,579
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He cut a deal with me.
What are you
talking about?</i></b></font>

870
00:30:29,662 --> 00:30:31,664
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>After you told him I was
involved with this thing,</i></b></font>

871
00:30:31,748 --> 00:30:33,082
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>he called me and
asked if I could do</i></b></font>

872
00:30:33,166 --> 00:30:34,250
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>something about his
friend Kevin.</i></b></font>

873
00:30:34,334 --> 00:30:37,045
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I said I'd look into it,
but he'd have to do
something for me.</i></b></font>

874
00:30:37,128 --> 00:30:38,546
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, you made some
bullshit promise</i></b></font>

875
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:39,923
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>with him in exchange
for doing that.</i></b></font>

876
00:30:40,006 --> 00:30:41,007
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It wasn't bullshit.</i></b></font>

877
00:30:41,090 --> 00:30:43,343
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't work for the
SEC, Harvey.</i></b></font>

878
00:30:43,426 --> 00:30:44,928
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I put away real criminals.</i></b></font>

879
00:30:45,011 --> 00:30:46,513
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And the person who put
away Kevin Miller</i></b></font>

880
00:30:46,596 --> 00:30:49,015
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>knows that it's worth it
to let a drunk driver out</i></b></font>

881
00:30:49,098 --> 00:30:50,767
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>as long as it means
keeping a murderer in.</i></b></font>

882
00:30:50,850 --> 00:30:53,186
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And to hell with what
happens to Mike.</i></b></font>

883
00:30:53,603 --> 00:30:55,730
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, he went in there with
his eyes wide open.</i></b></font>

884
00:30:55,813 --> 00:30:57,482
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And Gallo can't do
anything to him anyway,</i></b></font>

885
00:30:57,565 --> 00:30:58,691
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because he's getting
out tonight.</i></b></font>

886
00:30:58,775 --> 00:31:00,610
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Don't you get it?
Mike's not going
to be safe tonight</i></b></font>

887
00:31:00,693 --> 00:31:02,737
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>or any other night, because
Gallo can get to him</i></b></font>

888
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:04,197
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>whether he's
behind bars or not.</i></b></font>

889
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:06,324
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Well, like I said,
Harvey.</i></b></font>

890
00:31:06,449 --> 00:31:08,826
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>He knew what he was getting
into when he came to me.</i></b></font>

891
00:31:14,832 --> 00:31:16,459
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Hey, where have
you been all day?</i></b></font>

892
00:31:19,170 --> 00:31:20,630
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I've been doing what I
said I was going to do.</i></b></font>

893
00:31:21,631 --> 00:31:22,799
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm getting you out.</i></b></font>

894
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:24,634
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're kidding.</i></b></font>

895
00:31:24,717 --> 00:31:26,135
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Do I look like
I'm kidding?</i></b></font>

896
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,721
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>So, take that phone
of yours, call Jill,</i></b></font>

897
00:31:28,805 --> 00:31:31,182
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and tell her you're
coming home. Tonight.</i></b></font>

898
00:31:31,766 --> 00:31:33,893
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't believe it.
You really did that for me?</i></b></font>

899
00:31:34,477 --> 00:31:35,645
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I did.</i></b></font>

900
00:31:36,145 --> 00:31:37,564
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What about you?</i></b></font>

901
00:31:39,232 --> 00:31:40,483
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm getting out with you.</i></b></font>

902
00:31:46,739 --> 00:31:47,907
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>(CHUCKLES)</i></b></font>

903
00:31:49,367 --> 00:31:50,493
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What?</i></b></font>

904
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,245
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I...</i></b></font>

905
00:31:52,328 --> 00:31:53,580
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I just can't believe
I'm going to be tucking</i></b></font>

906
00:31:53,663 --> 00:31:54,998
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>my kids into
bed tonight.</i></b></font>

907
00:31:55,957 --> 00:31:57,458
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't believe I'm
going to see Rachel.</i></b></font>

908
00:32:00,086 --> 00:32:01,504
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I can't thank you
enough, Mike.</i></b></font>

909
00:32:03,423 --> 00:32:04,424
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>(KNOCKING)</i></b></font>

910
00:32:04,507 --> 00:32:06,175
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>All right, let's go.</i></b></font>

911
00:32:06,634 --> 00:32:07,927
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It's about time.</i></b></font>

912
00:32:08,011 --> 00:32:09,971
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Not you, Ross.
Just Miller.</i></b></font>

913
00:32:10,054 --> 00:32:11,806
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What? What are you
talking about?</i></b></font>

914
00:32:11,889 --> 00:32:13,141
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm getting out, too.</i></b></font>

915
00:32:13,224 --> 00:32:16,060
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm following orders,
and my orders are
to bring him out.</i></b></font>

916
00:32:16,144 --> 00:32:17,353
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Not you.</i></b></font>

917
00:32:18,313 --> 00:32:19,606
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You did this.</i></b></font>

918
00:32:20,481 --> 00:32:21,733
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I didn't do shit,</i></b></font>

919
00:32:21,816 --> 00:32:23,985
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>but I sure as hell am going
to take advantage of it.</i></b></font>

920
00:32:26,863 --> 00:32:28,156
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I'm not leaving
without Mike.</i></b></font>

921
00:32:29,157 --> 00:32:30,700
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Yeah, you are.</i></b></font>

922
00:32:30,783 --> 00:32:32,285
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I don't care
if I have to drag</i></b></font>

923
00:32:32,368 --> 00:32:34,037
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>your ass out
of here myself.</i></b></font>

924
00:32:34,120 --> 00:32:36,122
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You're leaving
right now.</i></b></font>

925
00:32:37,540 --> 00:32:39,459
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, good,
you're here.
What the hell's going on?</i></b></font>

926
00:32:39,542 --> 00:32:41,961
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You said you'd
reinstate the deal
if Mike dropped his suit.</i></b></font>

927
00:32:42,045 --> 00:32:43,296
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And I did.
Bullshit.</i></b></font>

928
00:32:43,379 --> 00:32:45,465
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You pulled his deal and now
he's in there all alone.</i></b></font>

929
00:32:45,548 --> 00:32:46,799
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now if you don't pick
up the phone...</i></b></font>

930
00:32:46,883 --> 00:32:48,635
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Harvey, I didn't
pull anything.</i></b></font>

931
00:32:48,718 --> 00:32:49,886
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What?</i></b></font>

932
00:32:49,969 --> 00:32:51,137
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Mike called me
and told me to hold off</i></b></font>

933
00:32:51,220 --> 00:32:52,680
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>his paperwork until
tomorrow morning.</i></b></font>

934
00:32:52,764 --> 00:32:54,390
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Why the hell would
he do that, Sean?</i></b></font>

935
00:32:54,474 --> 00:32:56,267
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Because he has a plan and
he didn't want you to know.</i></b></font>

936
00:32:56,351 --> 00:32:57,894
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I don't care
what his plan is.</i></b></font>

937
00:32:57,935 --> 00:32:59,437
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You do...
Listen. He
doesn't want you</i></b></font>

938
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,980
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>to know because he didn't
want you to stop it.</i></b></font>

939
00:33:01,064 --> 00:33:03,399
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Now that you can't,
he's going to need our
help to bring it home.</i></b></font>

940
00:33:17,747 --> 00:33:18,956
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>(DOOR OPENS)</i></b></font>

941
00:33:20,792 --> 00:33:22,752
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Thanks, Jimbo.
Why don't you go ahead</i></b></font>

942
00:33:22,835 --> 00:33:24,921
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>and give me and Mike here
a little privacy?</i></b></font>

943
00:33:29,801 --> 00:33:31,386
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What do you want, Gallo?</i></b></font>

944
00:33:31,469 --> 00:33:34,013
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>That's a stupid question
after what you pulled
at my parole hearing.</i></b></font>

945
00:33:34,097 --> 00:33:36,182
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You didn't deserve
to get out.
Neither did you.</i></b></font>

946
00:33:36,265 --> 00:33:37,600
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And now,
you're not going to.</i></b></font>

947
00:33:38,142 --> 00:33:39,727
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>What, you're going to
kill me in this cell?</i></b></font>

948
00:33:41,145 --> 00:33:42,563
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>There are guards out there.</i></b></font>

949
00:33:43,523 --> 00:33:45,566
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>It just doesn't sink in
for you, does it?</i></b></font>

950
00:33:45,650 --> 00:33:47,568
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Those guards out
there work for me.</i></b></font>

951
00:33:47,777 --> 00:33:49,362
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You see, Mike,
I wasn't going to let</i></b></font>

952
00:33:49,445 --> 00:33:51,489
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>what happened last time
happen this time.</i></b></font>

953
00:33:52,031 --> 00:33:53,449
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No one's going to come
run helping you</i></b></font>

954
00:33:53,533 --> 00:33:55,076
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>at the last second
because they're all</i></b></font>

955
00:33:55,159 --> 00:33:57,203
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>locked up tight
in their bunks.</i></b></font>

956
00:33:57,286 --> 00:33:59,080
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And irony of ironies,</i></b></font>

957
00:33:59,163 --> 00:34:01,457
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>because of some
prisoners' rights lawsuit</i></b></font>

958
00:34:01,541 --> 00:34:02,792
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>way back when,</i></b></font>

959
00:34:03,126 --> 00:34:04,544
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>there are no
cameras in cells.</i></b></font>

960
00:34:04,627 --> 00:34:05,670
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Wait, wait, wait,
wait, wait, wait.</i></b></font>

961
00:34:05,753 --> 00:34:06,963
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No, the time for
waiting is done.</i></b></font>

962
00:34:07,046 --> 00:34:08,047
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>(MIKE GRUNTING)</i></b></font>

963
00:34:08,965 --> 00:34:10,383
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No. No, no, no,
no, no, no.</i></b></font>

964
00:34:10,466 --> 00:34:12,051
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>I meant, don't you
want to hear about</i></b></font>

965
00:34:12,135 --> 00:34:13,428
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>the camera
that's in here?</i></b></font>

966
00:34:13,511 --> 00:34:14,554
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Bullshit.</i></b></font>

967
00:34:14,637 --> 00:34:16,764
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Smile, you
son of a bitch.</i></b></font>

968
00:34:16,973 --> 00:34:18,057
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>No!</i></b></font>

969
00:34:19,475 --> 00:34:21,310
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>You did not keep yourself
in here just to do this.</i></b></font>

970
00:34:21,394 --> 00:34:22,603
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Oh, yeah, Frank, I did.</i></b></font>

971
00:34:22,687 --> 00:34:24,564
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>And now, all those guards
that aren't in your pocket?</i></b></font>

972
00:34:24,647 --> 00:34:26,190
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>They're watching
this right now.</i></b></font>

973
00:34:26,274 --> 00:34:28,693
